SUMMARY:Deadline: LOOP City Screen / DOM Art Residence: Open Call for Video
  Artists (Barcelona)
DESCRIPTION:Open call for international video artists to present work in ur
 ban space during LOOP Festival Barcelona\, via the City Screen program wit
 h DOM Art Residence. Selected artists receive curatorial guidance\, produc
 tion support\, and screenings across public screens and facades in Barcelo
 na. DETAILS PARTIALLY UNVERIFIED: sourced from the Contemporary Lynx summe
 r 2026 open-call roundup\; confirm terms on the organizer's page before ap
 plying. Deadline 15 July 2026.\n\nOrganisation: LOOP Festival / DOM Art Re
 sidence\nLocation: Barcelona\, Spain\; work screened on public screens and
  facades across the city.\nAward: Curatorial guidance\, production support
 \, and screening of selected video work across Barcelona public screens du
 ring LOOP Festival. Fee not stated.\nDuration: Screenings during LOOP Fest
 ival Barcelona 2026.\n\nMore: https://contemporarylynx.co.uk/10-open-calls
 -to-apply-for-in-summer-2026?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_med
 ium=referral
URL:https://contemporarylynx.co.uk/10-open-calls-to-apply-for-in-summer-202
 6?utm_source=artificialnouveaugrantdesk&utm_medium=referral
LOCATION:Barcelona\, Spain\; work screened on public screens and facades ac
 ross the city.
END:VEVENT
